{"tid":912955,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"血的控訴！　12歲女生自縊　腳跟𠝹「R.I.P.」　遺寫滿欺凌者字條","createTime":"2018-11-23T05:15:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-23T19:22:13.000Z","uid":212399,"like":96,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"b135acc37c1d87e803d64339c51c5b2768707a11","tid":912955,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:15:27.000Z","msg":"英國12歲女學生史嘉達遜（Jessica Scatterson）去年4月因為被欺凌而上吊自殺，警方發現她不但在腳跟𠝹了「R.I.P.」的字眼，還留下了一張寫滿欺凌者名字的字條。當地法庭周一（19日）在沃靈頓市政廳（Warrington Town Hall）舉行聽證會，以便調查史嘉達遜自殺的真相。<br />\n史嘉達遜自殺當晚，有同學發現她在Facebook上載了一雙腳的照片，並寫下令人心寒的句子，於是馬上報警求助。<br />\n警方到了史嘉達遜的寓所後，叫醒了其41歲的爸爸，沒多久她的睡房裏便傳來一下尖叫聲，爸爸打開睡房門，發現史嘉達遜已沒有呼吸，右腳跟𠝹有「R.I.P.」的字眼，身旁全是她的玩具，還有一些關於死亡及自殺的手寫字條和圖畫，上面寫滿了欺凌者的名字；警方又在史嘉達遜的平板電腦內發現她和朋友互傳的惡意訊息，另有一張一名女孩的樣子被刮去的集體照。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2121656/org/afdfd1a63df217c0bebdd8d5fdcf63d8.jpg/FB23eKyrMnFULQFdU87P8q1kq_tiBVIH_WhzAv1ocwI?v=w480\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2121656%2Forg%2Fafdfd1a63df217c0bebdd8d5fdcf63d8.jpg%2FFB23eKyrMnFULQFdU87P8q1kq_tiBVIH_WhzAv1ocwI%3Fv%3Dw480&h=df05c156&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2121657/org/8f904ccc15f4377636db1fe09d3c84bd.jpg/7HuSq3aN6if3-qkDWPOZtTWWsHKgOAK18iaLgvImi4I?v=w480\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2121657%2Forg%2F8f904ccc15f4377636db1fe09d3c84bd.jpg%2F7HuSq3aN6if3-qkDWPOZtTWWsHKgOAK18iaLgvImi4I%3Fv%3Dw480&h=2432629a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2121666/org/ca926b80f9d746446bb90285f7f2ff8f.jpg/ZCbdAPb9SWKNJhWRuecPydxyV8Kz4recYMQ_7WDEP-0?v=w480\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2121666%2Forg%2Fca926b80f9d746446bb90285f7f2ff8f.jpg%2FZCbdAPb9SWKNJhWRuecPydxyV8Kz4recYMQ_7WDEP-0%3Fv%3Dw480&h=559be332&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2121667/org/de03f330fed53baea26c12696ae69627.jpg/pru_fdx8Iym0KlCkPFhgoDqCusrG5RTkKWZwcilmcHI?v=w480\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2121667%2Forg%2Fde03f330fed53baea26c12696ae69627.jpg%2Fpru_fdx8Iym0KlCkPFhgoDqCusrG5RTkKWZwcilmcHI%3Fv%3Dw480&h=632c9711&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聽證會上透露，原來2016年史嘉達遜在學校和一名女孩發生過爭執，臉部慘被抓傷，學校老師證實真有其事，但當時沒有視作是欺凌來處理；警方也有介入，但因為查不出是誰出手打人在先，結果不了了之；該名和史嘉達遜發生爭執的女生，名字也有出現在史嘉達遜寫的自殺字條上，然而該女生接受警方問話時強調自己沒有參與欺凌，並謂與史嘉達遜「一直過得很好」。<br />\n另外，有人在聽證會上透露，史嘉達遜曾經自殘，但她從沒有告訴家長或老師。老師畢朗（Sarah Baron）稱：「史嘉達遜較同齡孩子要負擔更多。」因為她的爸爸患有情緒問題，有時返家後「會立刻回房大哭」，故大部分的日常家務如煮食和打掃清潔等都落在史嘉達遜身上。一名駐校牧師說：「史嘉達遜就像隻小母雞，責任感很強，不論在家還是和朋友相處，都很關心她的爸爸，並為他的情緒問題感到憂心。」"},{"pid":"7e5cee2dc89cc0fc5836963b760fe52ee3de540c","tid":912955,"uid":59898,"like":281,"dislike":7,"score":274,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:16:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁靚女都要俾人bully,rip"},{"pid":"1da49b427914b66d9f925f3fba40d231d4066604","tid":912955,"uid":3457,"like":27,"dislike":2,"score":25,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:18:08.000Z","msg":"我覺得依類事好快比人拍成鬼片"},{"pid":"f4015762015161cf66efd6e8a029d47ef53fefee","tid":912955,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:18:21.000Z","msg":"y<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"943d8d8f5113e986ebc0efbdcb407f5102f5c0b6","tid":912955,"uid":212399,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:19:11.000Z","msg":"點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0044c04c06bdce4950e9f9828133a73131dd0fb","tid":912955,"uid":73613,"like":172,"dislike":8,"score":164,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-23T05:20:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"69dd1e79f8104905ab7212e35c01f7ed46e3250c","tid":912955,"uid":177089,"lik